ì´ë¥¼ ìœ„í•´ì„œ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Continuation</code>ì˜ ì œë„¤ë¦­ íƒ€ì…ì´ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">User</code>ê°€ ì•„ë‹ˆë¼ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Any?</code>ì´ë‹¤.</p>
